      "statement": "Multi-tier FM-match: for tier \u03c4=0,1,...,R\u22121, run FM-match on yet-unmatched active highs with a fresh free domain. Each tier matches \u2264\u230an/e\u230b highs. Tag matched high by (\u03c4, local_rank) \u2208 [R]\u00d7[\u230an/e\u230b]. If R\u00b7\u230an/e\u230b \u2264 K_max (deployed R\u226470), tags fit the high budget. Every high that possesses at least one free-1 e-set is matched within at most |H| tiers (domain reset each tier).",
